audit.prompt:
Review the following PDDL domain and problem generated by the planner:
{initial_pddl_plan}
Check for temporal/causal consistency and ensure all actions are correctly defined according to the environment rules:
{environment->public_information}
If corrections are needed, provide the revised PDDL domain and problem. If the provided PDDL is flawless, repeat it exactly. Do not add any bookkeeping shortcuts. Enclose the corrected PDDL domain between <domain></domain> tags, and the PDDL problem between <problem></problem> tags.
